ally every asset class and investment style our team of more than  investment professionals and support staff work in offices around the world collectively overseeing more than  billion in assets under management as of december  as part of our asset management team you will work with some of the industry’s leading experts in delivering investment solutions that help our clients achieve their goals investment banking   corporations governments and institutions around the world trust us to help them make critical business decisions navigate strategic transactions and raise capital to fund growth and infrastructure join us and have the opportunity to shape innovative deals that are transforming today’s corporate landscape organizational structure we serve our clients through three regionally focused divisions swiss universal bank international wealth management and asia pacific these regional businesses are supported by two divisions specialized in investment banking capabilities global markets and investment banking  capital markets our organizational structure reflects the global nature of our company and our strategy for growing our core businesses  swiss universal bank offers private banking and wealth management corporate banking investment banking and retail banking for individuals corporations and institutions domiciled in switzerland international wealth management provides wealth management products and services to private clients within most of europe latin america the middle east and africa asia pacific provides integrated private banking and investment banking financial solutions to wealthy individuals institutional investors and corporate clients in the asia pacific region drawing on credit suisse’s global resources to capture the region’s rapid wealth creation and growth in ultrahighnetworth uhnw global markets specializes in equities and fixed income products and services including sales trading prime brokerage underwriting and research clients include financial institutions corporations governments and institutional investors investment banking and capital markets focuses on advisory services related to mergers and acquisitions divestitures takeover defense business restructures spinoffs and debt and equity underwriting this division works with corporations financial institutions financial sponsors ultrahighnetworth individuals and sovereign clients all five of our business divisions are supported by our centralized corporate functions corporate functions the corporate functions provide support to our business divisions and help guarantee the smooth and efficient operation of our clientfacing businesses our corporate functions include our human resources branding  communications compliance and regulatory affairs finance general counsel operations risk and technology it teams these teams manage a variety of fastpaced challenges as they provide highquality costeffective services to our business divisions  technology it our technology it team is one of our corporate functions and at over  professionals the technology division is larger than many technology companies the technology team is a critical commercial differentiator and creates products and services that enable the flow of financial information across the globe explore our technology programs locations credit suisse is a truly global organization with offices in approximately  countries learn more about where we are located by clicking on the regions below americas bahamas nassau brazil sao paolo canada calgary toronto chile santiago mexico mexico city usa chicago houston los angeles new york raleigh and san francisco asia pacific australia melbourne sydney china beijing shanghai hong kong india bangalore mumbai pune indonesia jakarta japan tokyo malaysia kuala lumpur philippines manila singapore south korea seoul taiwan taipei thailand bangkok europe middle east and africa austria vienna bahrain manama egypt cairo france paris germany frankfurt channel isla